# Redux Rules

## Store Structure

Root State

{
  search: SearchState,
  settings: SettingsState
}

---

## SearchState

{
  results: SearchResult[],
  loading: boolean,
  error: string | null
}

---

## SettingsState

{
  items: WebsiteItem[],
  loading: boolean,
  error: string | null
}

---

## Async Actions

Search:

searchNews(query)

Settings:

loadWebsites()

createWebsite(url)

updateWebsite(item)

deleteWebsite(guid)

---

## Selectors

Create selectors for all state access.

Components should never directly access deep state structures.